<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Nematodes, or roundworms, live in practically all habitats and influence soil fertility, food safety, and other aspects of animal &amp; plant health. The Nematology minor supports careers in plant and agricultural nematology and provides valuable information for careers in animal, plant, and soil health.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
